summary: A conversion of the ESO Altmer Armor for CBBE Bodyslide.
descriptionHtml:
This is ESO Altmer Armor for CBBE Bodyslide. It requires the original ESO Altmer Armor mod. There may be a bit of clipping with some bodyslides.

Requirements
[list]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49015/?]Bodyslide 2[/url]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/64532/?]ESO Altmer Armor by NewerMind43[/url]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?]CBBE[/url]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53996/?]HDT Physics[/url]
[/list]
Special thanks to the people behind Bodyslide 2 and Outfit Studio, the ESO Altmer Armor by NewerMind43, and HydrogensaysHDT for HDT. And of course to Bethesda for The Elder Scrolls.
author: Raelfallen
